cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper deals with improving predictions in computer vision tasks using deep neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses multi-task learning, which falls under the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with ambiguity in predictions, which is a problem in artificial intelligence, making cs.AI a likely sub-category. The paper also discusses text descriptions of images, which falls under the sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper deals with video summarization, which falls under the sub-category cs.MM (Multimedia).
